description: For sale: $349,999. Beautiful 40-acre hobby or horse farm, located on a quiet country road, with the scenic Moose Horn River flowing through the property. The property offers a ranch-style home with three bedrooms and 1+ baths. With a beautiful second story bathroom. The home also offers gorgeous floors, fireplace, formal dining room, a welcoming front entryway and gorgeous tongue-in-groove pine ceilings! In addition to the garage, there's a tack room in the barn, along with stalls, several loafing sheds, covered machinery building and a chicken coop! Much of this property is fenced and currently horses and mules are kept on the land. There is one field that could be used for producing alfalfa. A dditional 40 acres is also for sale just west of the house accessed via private easement. This 40 acres gives the current owner access to hundreds of acres of riding trails on both his land and an abandoned railroad grade.Also great hunting, XC Sking, 4 wheeling, snowmobiling  on this 40 acres.

description: Recently sold: $190,000. Welcome home to this beautifully updated 2 bedroom, 1 bath home on a 10-acre property in Barnum. This home features an updated kitchen with new Hickory cabinets, floors and Stainless-steel appliances. Additional home updates include new carpet, windows, siding and roof. Outside features include six newly fenced in acres.  With four pastures, a heated outbuilding, run-in shed and a round pen, this property would be ideal for a Hobby farm. It is only minutes away from the Soo Line Trail and state land which makes it perfect for horseback riding, atv riding and hunting. With an egress window installed, the basement is ready to include a third bedroom.  Plum and a variety of apple trees add an abundance of wildlife to this home's outdoor beauty. Make this home your own!

Recently sold: $398,000. Gorgeous lake property with 200 ft of sand shoreline on Sandy lake in Blackhoof Twp in Barnum. Privacy on 2.62 acres level lot. Very good size well maintained home with walkout basement - 4 Bedrooms (2 on the main and 2 on the upper level), 5 Bathrooms, 3 wood burning fire places, 2 heat pumps with heat & cool option, beautiful living room with hardwood floor and bay window facing the lake. Kitchen / dining room combo with granite counter-tops, custom made cabinets with one wall of darker cabinets and appliances new in 2018. It walks out to a large lake deck with nice awning. On the lower level you'll have large rec room, family room with fire place with a blower, office/craft room, sauna with changing room and bath with shower. House has electric dual fuel heat with two heat pumps with cooling option as well. Attached 2 car insulated garage & another 2 car detached garage, carport. Property has drain field septic system and drilled well. Too many great features to list! Not a drive by. Beautifully landscaped property with apple, cherry and maple trees. You will love to watch spectacular sunsets over the lake! Come take a closer look and you will not be disappointed.

Recently sold: $150,000. 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath manufactured home on 4.5 acres. The lot is mostly wooded with a great view from the home. Comes with a large two stall detached garage that is insulated and has a built in work bench.

description: Recently sold: $169,900. Harvest the benefits of this country home just outside city limits. Let's start with the yard...it's over 2 of the prettiest acres you will ever see. The flower gardens await you. It has a blacktop driveway and large pole barn and a spot for RV parking with hook-ups. There is a attached garage with breezeway and plenty of room for pets of all shapes to run. Now that you've found your new home, please enjoy the updated kitchen with enough room for two tables, smaller breakfast and larger dining. You can also enjoy the patio. Now, the living room is awesome with an open floor plan, all new windows throughout the house, new carpet & flooring. The list just goes on. One large bedroom in the basement could be two if needed. This home sits on top of the bike trail. It doesn't get much better! Brokered And Advertised By: Coldwell Banker East West II Listing Agent: Patry Truman
